{"id": "6981", "post": "<div class=\"post-6981 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-18thbirthday tag-ipv6 tag-italy tag-milan tag-openvz tag-prometeus-net tag-ssd tag-xen tag-xenpv\" id=\"post-6981\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/prometeus-18th-birthday-special-xen-and-openvz-from-6-90month-in-milan/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Prometeus \u2013 18th Birthday Special \u2013 Xen and OpenVZ from $6.90/month in Milan</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/18thbirthday/\" rel=\"tag\">18thbirthday</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ipv6/\" rel=\"tag\">ipv6</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/italy/\" rel=\"tag\">italy</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/milan/\" rel=\"tag\">milan</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/prometeus-net/\" rel=\"tag\">Prometeus.net</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ssd/\" rel=\"tag\">ssd</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xenpv/\" rel=\"tag\">xenpv</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> May 24, 2015 @ 1:00 am, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/site/index.php\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTgxIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE4MSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot alignnone size-medium wp-image-6984\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/prometeus-net-2015-05-22-16-52-43-300x181.png\" alt=\"prometeus net 2015-05-22 16-52-43\" width=\"300\" height=\"181\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/prometeus-net-2015-05-22-16-52-43-300x181.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/prometeus-net-2015-05-22-16-52-43-1024x617.png 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/prometeus-net-2015-05-22-16-52-43.png 1169w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></a>Each year, these posts get more special to write, but at 18, it\u2019s a very special one. Salvatore has shared these offers with the community to celebrate <a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/site/index.php\">Prometeus</a>\u2018 <em>18th</em> birthday!</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>XP18</strong><p></p><ul><li>1.8GB RAM</li><li>4 CPU cores</li><li>180GB HDD space</li><li>1.8TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>2x IPv6</li><li>XenPV/SolusVM</li><li>\u20ac6/month ($6.90)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=136\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VZSSD18</strong><p></p><ul><li>1.8GB RAM</li><li>1GB vSwap</li><li>4 CPU cores</li><li>50GB SSD space</li><li>1.8TB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>4x IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>\u20ac18/6 months ($21.60)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=137\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Yes, I know what you\u2019re thinking. This provider is older than most people are that are running some \u201cproviders\u201d on LET. And that is worth a lot of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>very big heartfelt congratulations</strong></span> from all of us!</p><p>1997 was the year that I got introduced to the internet, actually. Dialing up each morning around 06:30 with my dad to track the Withbread Round the World Race progress. And Salvatore was busy doing hosting! It\u2019s incredible. But what\u2019s even more incredible is that they are still around today offering simply stellar service and servers at insanely low prices. I\u2019m not just talking about their regular offering, but also about iwStack: the first real cloud within LowEnd price range!</p><p>I could now bother you with the details of the massive host nodes that Prometeus uses, but instead I\u2019m going to give you this coupon for 18% off of <em>any</em> invoice (one invoice only)! The coupon is <strong><b>18OneOff</b></strong>! It\u2019s valid for all servers other than the ones above, so it\u2019s also valid for iwStack credits.</p><p>I invite you, please, to share your congratulations in the comments for Salvatore and the rest of Prometeus for having been with us for 18 years!</p><p><span id=\"more-6981\"></span></p><p>Prometeus\u2019 has revamped their OpenVZ offering, now only offering high-memory SSD-based OpenVZ boxes, with the VZSSD18 above being the smallest one available. You can order the 1.8GB OpenVZ server until the end of the month, so be quick to grab one!</p><p>Payments can be made using PayPal, credit cards through PayPal, and EU bank transfer. All servers are self-managed, meaning you are responsible to keep the server running and Prometeus is responsible for keeping the host node running. For all the details on what is allowed and what is not, among other things, please have a look at their <a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/site/tos.php\">Terms of Service</a> and <a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/site/privacy.php\">Privacy Policy</a>!</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/site/network.php\">Looking glass for all locations!</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-back